node.text: We just had an 80lb blacktip shark bust our terminal tackle. Can you name another species of fish that weighs 80lbs that can destroy terminal tackle like this with around 10lbs of drag? #blacktiph #fishing #terminaltackle #tackle #busted #hook #rig #blacktip #blacktipshark #surffishing

node.text: In this video, I go fishing with Florida Fish and Wildlife Conservation Commission on Lake Weohyakapka using electricity to catch giant fish! Our goal was to find a 10lb bass. We caught a monster 10lb and 12lb bass!!

node.title: Using ELECTRICITY to Catch GIANT Fish

node.text: In this IGTV video, I go fishing for ballyhoo with fellow creator Paul Cuffaro. Ballyhoo are a very unique fish that have a bone or beak on their bottom jaw and they are great bait!

node.text: We just launched our BlacktipH Platinum Club for our most dedicated fans! We will be uploading exclusive content to the Platinum Club that won’t be see on any other platform. Also will be giving away monthly fishing trips to members, merch discounts, and much more! Click the link in our bio for more details! #blacktiph

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BlacktipH in YouTube with @youtube, and @blacktiphbrand. May be an image of text that says 'BILLION VIEWS'.

node.text: We just hit 1 billion views on YouTube!! 🙌 This is an incredible milestone for a fishing show! If you told me back in 2006, when I began uploading, that we would one day reach a billion views, I wouldn't believe you! Thank you for all the support! #blacktiph #fishingshow #youtube #milestone @blacktiphbrand

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BlacktipH in Cypress Cove Marina & Lodge with @yesjulz, @d_riley40, @louisthornton22, @jakejorgs, @tidelineboats, and @blacktiphbrand. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: After an intense battle, @cmpulisic finally caught and released his first shark. Christian’s stamina is next level folks! Caught and released with @docb22 and @emadgg_ #blacktiph #fishing #shark #sharkfishing #catchandrelease #florida #offshorefishing #football #soccer @blacktiphbrand

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by BlacktipH on June 29, 2021 tagging @blacktiphhunter, @davis_bennett_, @docb22, @fishcolombia, and @joshua_jorgensen. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: Most fishermen dream of catching a world record-sized fish, especially a world record tarpon! We caught this massive Tarpon in Colombia with @fishcolombia and @docb22 in Bahía Solano. We had no idea how big this fish truly was until we got on some WIFI at the lodge and started doing some research. After speaking with @delphfishing and Raymond Douglas from @kingsailfishmounts and using the @bonefishtarpontrust tarpon weight calculator, we estimated that our fish was around 312lbs, beating the current world record by over 25lbs! We used a goggle eye for bait. Colombia has massive tarpon and if you want to catch one over 200lbs, I highly recommend booking a trip with @fishcolombia #blacktiph #fishing #tarpon #record #worldrecord #tarponfishing #colombia #pacific #ocean #fish #monsterfish 📷 @davis_bennett_

node.text: After years of talking about it, @donaldjtrumpjr and I finally got to catch some monster Goliath Groupers together with @docb22. We caught one that was pushing 500lbs and a bunch over 300lbs! #blacktiph #fishing #goliathgrouper #grouper #florida #offshore #giant #monster #fish #goliath #nature #ocean #trump 📸 @blacktiphhunter

node.text: Caught a monster Goliath Grouper this week with @bfielder and @johnwhite4 from @chickfila. We caught over 10 Goliath Groupers throughout the day and this fish was by far the largest! Estimated weight was between 450-500lbs #blacktiph #fishing #goliathgrouper #grouper #florida #chickfila #fish #giant #monster #nature #ocean #goliath
